lead_paragraph: Prolific Athletic Bilbao striker Aritz Aduriz has been named in the Spain squad for this month's home World Cup qualifier against Macedonia and the friendly against England at Wembley.

headline.print_headline: Veteran Aduriz and Mata Back in Spain Squad
